[06/12/2017 13:58:31] <font color="#ffff00">Gus, amigo.</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:31] <font color="#ffff00">Gus.</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:35] <font color="#0000ff">(Disparos)</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:50] <font color="#ffff00">¡Volved al bosque!</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:50] <font color="#ffff00">¡Volved al bosque!</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:54] <font color="#ffff00">¡Atrás, al bosque!</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:54] <font color="#ffff00">¡Vamos, al bosque!</font>
[06/12/2017 13:58:57] <font color="#0000ff">(Disparos)</font>
[06/12/2017 13:59:23] <font color="#ffff00">¡Volvamos al fuerte!</font>
[06/12/2017 13:59:23] <font color="#ffff00">¡Volvamos al fuerte!</font>
[06/12/2017 13:59:26] <font color="#ffff00">Vamos, chico.</font>
[06/12/2017 13:59:26] <font color="#ffff00">Ya has hecho bastante.</font>
[06/12/2017 13:59:30] <font color="#ffff00">¡Volved al fuerte!</font>
