[06/12/2017 22:38:41] <font color="#ffff00">Sé valiente, Ann.</font>
[06/12/2017 22:38:48] <font color="#00ff00">Tony.</font>
[06/12/2017 22:38:49] <font color="#00ff00">Ten cuidado.</font>
[06/12/2017 22:39:21] <font color="#00ffff">Sabes que siempre me alegro</font>
